|  | |____| |__| |                         |
|   \_____|_____/                          |
|                                          |
|  cd gives you the power to move.         |
|                                          |
|  cd                                      |
|  This takes you the home directory       |
|                                          |
|  cd ../                                  |
|  This moves you back a directory         |
|                                          |
|  cd hidey-hole                           |
|  This will move you inside hidey-hole,   |
|  assuming you are next to it             |
|                                          |
|  cd ~/wood/treehouse                     |
|  This will move you ~/wood/treehouse     |
|  regardless of your current position     |
\                                          /
 `----------------------------------------'
